		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_TADC2_POMNI_FIRSTGREETING_1">
			<Text>Hello! My name is Pomni, and I... I'm pleased to meet you, I guess? I'm completely stuck in this place, you don't know a way out, do you?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_TADC2_POMNI_DEFEATED_1">
			<Text>I'm finished! How do I... take this... headset off?!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_TADC2_POMNI_GREETING_POLITE_HELLO_1">
			<Text>Hi again! My friends have just finished making a cake. Would you join us?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_TADC2_POMNI_GREETING_NEUTRAL_HELLO_1">
			<Text>What time period is this supposed to be again?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_TADC2_POMNI_GREETING_HOSTILE_HELLO_1">
			<Text>Wait, wait. Was that an exit door I just saw? I'd take any opportunity to leave this conversation!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_TADC2_POMNI_HOSTILE_AGGRESSIVE_MILITARY_WARNING_1">
			<Text>I swear I saw a lot of units gathering outside. Please tell me you're not going to do what I think you're about to do.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_TADC2_POMNI_HOSTILE_HUMAN_SMALL_ARMY">
			<Text>I may not even remember my own name, but in my opinion, you should be trying harder to remember to build up a military... Just a heads up.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_TADC2_POMNI_EXPANSION_SERIOUS_WARNING_1">
			<Text>Hey, what do you think you're up to?! Stay away from us!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_TADC2_POMNI_REQUEST">
			<Text>My friends and I are in some trouble. Could you lend a hand, please...?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_TADC2_POMNI_LUXURY_TRADE">
			<Text>Kinger is just obsessed with those spare resources you have... Can we trade for them?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_TADC2_POMNI_ATTACKED_BETRAYED">
			<Text>OH, YOU (%$!#)HOLE!</Text>
